HEADWORD: Stillicide
<hw>Stil"li*cide</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stillicidium</ets>; <ets>stilla</ets> a drop + <ets>cadere</ets> to
fall.]</ety> <def>A continual falling or succession of drops; rain water
falling from the eaves.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

